summary: How the Reylo kiss should go
body:
How the Reylo kiss should go

I know everyone’s all, “Oh it should be so sweet and angsty and fluffy!”

But y'know what I want?

Anger kisses

Like, they’re saber battling, or arguing through the force connection, and they both stop for a second to take a breath and glare at each other. Then, BOOM, just a hate-fuelled, passion-filled make out session (a la Xander and Cordy)

summary:
So my siblings and I were watching TLJ (for the hundredth time I guess...)
And we came to the part during the aftermath of the...
body:
So my siblings and I were watching TLJ (for the hundredth time I guess…)

And we came to the part during the aftermath of the throne room fight (freaking gets me every time🤣😍) and THIS happened:

(My Baby) Ben Solo:… I want you to join me. Together we can bring a new order to the Galaxy.

(Precious) Rey: Please don’t do this. Please don’t go this way.

My little bro bro: YOU RUINED IT MAN! YOU RUINED IT!

We freaking died 😂😂

blog.title: Miit'alor
blog.description: I am a descriptivist linguist for the Mando'a language. I show what it can do, not what it MUST do. This is a place for discussion about Mando'a, and Mandalorian society and culture. Feel free to use the head cannons from this blog (or reblogged from others) in your RP or writing. All words and descriptions are taken from the mandoa.org Mandalorian Dictionary. Want to support this blog? Buy me a Kofi? OR buy some Mando'a themed items? Visit our Discord? Blog icon by Rina
